OL,6,FFamilies have told of their
OL,7,Fdetermination to ensure loved ones
OL,8,Flost during the Covid pandemic are not
OL,9,Fremembered as just a statistic.
OL,11,FThe next episode of UTV's award
OL,12,Fwinning current affairs programme 'Up
OL,13,FClose' examinesJthe evidence of the
OL,14,Frecent Covid inquiry, looking at how
OL,15,Fthe Stormont Executive and civil
OL,16,Fservice managed the crisis.
OL,18,FThe programme hears the powerful
OL,19,Fstories from three families affected
OL,20,Fwho lost loved onesJduring the
OL,21,Fpandemic.
