OL,6,FThe special investigation airs on
OL,7,FThursday 30 May at 10.45pm.
OL,9,FPresented by UTV's Niall Donnelly, the
OL,10,Fhour-long programme takes a deep dive
OL,11,Finto the three weeks' worth of
OL,12,Fevidence at the Northern Ireland stage
OL,13,Fof the UK Covid Inquiry and analyses
OL,14,Fthe shocking revelations uncovered
OL,15,Fduring the hearings including the
OL,16,Fpolitical division and tensions within
OL,17,Fgovernment.
