OL,6,FUTV's health reporter Deborah McAleese
OL,7,Freported on the pandemic and watched
OL,8,Fevery day of the inquiry as ministers,
OL,9,Fsenior civil servants and others gave
OL,10,Fevidence to the panel, facing tough
OL,11,Fquestions about their decision making
OL,12,Fat the time.
OL,14,FFor the special programme, Deborah
OL,15,Fexamined the evidence. She has
OL,16,Fproduced two reports which highlight
OL,17,Fhow the pandemic first appeared in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and how the Executive
OL,19,Fresponded in those early days.
