OL,6,FThe inquiry revealed WhatsApp messages
OL,7,Fbetween senior civil servants claiming
OL,8,Fthere was a lack of leadership in the
OL,9,FExecutive, and also apparent confusion
OL,10,Famong ministers as to who was actually
OL,11,Fin charge of the response.
OL,13,FDuring the inquiry, senior civil
OL,14,Fservants spoke of how little was known
OL,15,Fabout the virus in the early stages,
OL,16,Fthe lack of testing, and deaths of the
OL,17,Felderly in care homes.
OL,19,FThe inquiry also forced families to
OL,20,Frelive the trauma of the time.
