OL,6,FJulie McMurray's husband Robert
OL,7,Funderwent an operation. However during
OL,8,Frecovery in hospital he contracted
OL,9,FCovid.
OL,11,FJulie visited every day until lockdown
OL,12,Frestrictions prevented her attendance.
OL,13,FRobert suffered dementia and became
OL,14,Fmore stressed in hospital in his
OL,15,Ffamily's absence.
OL,17,F"I made a promise to look after him,"
OL,18,Fshe told UTV, "I told him we would get
OL,19,Fthrough it."
