OL,6,FShe said he thought he had done
OL,7,Fsomething wrong and pleaded with his
OL,8,Fwife and children to visit.
OL,10,F"He couldn't understand and he said
OL,11,F'why have you left me'."
OL,13,FWhen Julie finally got to see Robert
OL,14,Fhis condition has deteriorated.
OL,16,F"He could barely squeeze my hand....
OL,17,Fit was too late."
OL,19,FMichael Lusty's mother Peggy died
OL,20,Fduring the second wave.
