OL,6,F"And I thought, how are we still
OL,7,Frunning out of stuff in the second
OL,8,Fwave? A year later?J"A lot of people
OL,9,Ftalk about people dying in the nursing
OL,10,Fhomes, which is quite right. But a lot
OL,11,Fof people died in hospital and my
OL,12,Fmother was one of them and this should
OL,13,Fnever have went this far.
OL,15,F"The inquiry showed up a lot of
OL,16,Ffailings in our government."
OL,18,FBriege McEvoy's lost her 23-year-old
