OL,6,F"We were relying on our politicians to
OL,7,Fguide us," she said.
OL,9,F"Like, even whenever we think back to
OL,10,Fthe whole, let's eat out to help out.
OL,11,F"we were saying like, why, why are
OL,12,Fthey getting us to do this? Why are
OL,13,Fthey getting us to come out surely to
OL,14,FGod, that is only going to make things
OL,15,Fworse for everybody and that's exactly
OL,16,Fwhat it did.J"So, for them to make
OL,17,Fthese sort of decisions, they have
OL,18,Fcost lives .... it shouldn't have."
