OL,6,FDuring the programme, Niall will
OL,7,Fdiscuss the issues in the studio with
OL,8,FBrenda Doherty whoJrepresents bereaved
OL,9,Ffamilies, former civil servant Ann
OL,10,FWatt, Belfast Telegraph journalist and
OL,11,Fcommentator Sam McBride as well as
OL,12,Ffrom Deborah McAleese and UTV's
OL,13,FPolitical Editor Tracey Magee.JAlison
OL,14,Fsaid: "Having reported on the inquiry
OL,15,Ffor UTV Live, we felt it only right to
