OL,6,F"It laid bare the tensions at the
OL,7,Fheart of our government. This inquiry
OL,8,Fhas only scratched the surface and
OL,9,Fwhile nothing can be done to change
OL,10,Fwhat has happened, it's clear those
OL,11,Fimpacted most want lessons to be
OL,12,Flearned.
